culty Departments of faculty and staff will be reimbursed for the cost of the Gallagher insurance through their department Gallagher insurance Business managers or Travel Arrangers should contact The Office of Global Engagement for information at oge uic edu oge uic edu  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          Office of Global Engagement n         Other International Resources at UIC Center for Global Health Language and Culture Learning Center The Latino Cultural Center International Education at the College of Medicine Global Women s Health Fellowship Helpful Links Ask UIC U S  Department of State  International Travel Chicago Sister Cities International Chicago Office of the New Americans Chicago Visitors Contact               oge uic edu Social Media Accounts UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 